        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-2 flex-wrap-reverse align-items-center">
            <div class="col pe-lg-4">
                <img src="assets/Solutions/About_01.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="col ps-lg-4 ">
                <h4>@localizer["About_Tech_Title"]</h4>
                <p>
                    @localizer["About_Tech_P"]
                    @* LogiKCo provides custom IT solutions.  We’re here to help businesses and organizations improve and excel.

                    Think Better.  Think Faster.  Think Stronger.  Think LogiKCo. <br/>
                    In-person and remote training sessions as well as personal customer support are a given. Whether we’re delivering a custom solution, integrating systems, or supporting network infrastructure, our customer’s satisfaction is always our priority. *@
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-2 align-items-center">
            <div class="col pe-lg-4">
                <h4>@localizer["About_Good_Title"]</h4>
                <p>
                    @localizer["About_Good_P"]
                    @* LogiKCo’s IT team is here to help you develop a solution that works hard for your organization.  But good solutions need good design and great support.  Contact us today with any questions about existing or custom products.
                    <br/>
                    Think Innovative.  Think LogiKCo. *@
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col ps-lg-4">
                <img src="assets/Solutions/About_02.png" alt="">
